VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'me show you a little bit a behind-the-scenes look of what we do over in Las Vegas at our podcasting studio. So, we took these YoloCam S7s, and sometimes we\'ll shoot on higher-end cameras like the Sony FX3s, but those'

