[07:14] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'dollars at the time of recording this video. And then the lens will add another hundred bucks or so. So, for under a thousand dollars for each camera setup, you\'re getting this level of image quality, and you will never have to worry about overheating because of'

[07:26] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'the design of the S7. And for the studio build, we just ran HDMI cables directly into the YoloBox to get those 4K inputs, and it looks beautiful. And again, this is basically the same setup I have right here in my home office in Oregon, but'

